      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg/330px-Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"391\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg/500px-Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg/960px-Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Salvador_Dali_NYWTS.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Salvador Dalí, 1965</div></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salvador_Dal%C3%AD\">Salvador Dalí</a>, (May 11, 1904 – January 23, 1989)<br />\nwas a Spanish painter, graphic artist, writer, sculptor and stage designer, and one of the main representatives of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surrealism\">Surrealism</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Links\">Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:Salvador_Dal%C3%AD&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Salvador_Dal%C3%AD\">Salvador Dalí - Wikimedia Commons</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301022335\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.041 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.445 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 